#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kig; is <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/philosophy."
"html#AboutFreeSoftware\"> Free Software</ulink>. This means that its source "
"code is freely available on the Internet, and everyone can use it, read it, "
"modify it, and distribute it."
msgstr ""
"&kig; je <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/philosophy/philosophy."
"html#AboutFreeSoftware\"> prosta programska oprema</ulink>. To pomeni, da je "
"njegova izvorna koda prosto dostopna na internetu in jo lahko vsakdo "
"uporablja, bere, spreminja in distribuira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter I want to point out to you (the user) the rights that "
"&kig;'s license gives you. As with all free software, you are allowed (and "
"encouraged) to fix problems you encounter while using it, to add features "
"you miss, to distribute your modified program, and to send these "
"modifications back for inclusion through the review tools available for the "
"&kde; community."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju vas (uporabnika) želim opozoriti na pravice, ki vam jih daje "
"licenca &kig;. Kot pri vsej prosti programski opremi vam je dovoljeno (in "
"spodbujano), da odpravite težave, na katere naletite med uporabo, dodate "
"funkcije, ki jih pogrešate, distribuirate spremenjeni program in pošljete te "
"spremembe nazaj za vključitev prek orodij za pregledovanje, ki so na voljo "
"za &kde; skupnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are uncertain of your rights to use this software, or other people's "
"right to use any modifications you make to this program &etc;, please read "
"the license. You can find it in the <filename>COPYING</filename> file in the "
"&kig; source tree or the license link in the <guilabel>About &kig;</"
"guilabel> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če niste prepričani o svojih pravicah za uporabo te programske opreme ali o "
"pravici drugih ljudi za uporabo kakršnih koli sprememb, ki jih naredite v "
"tem programu itd., preberite licenco. Najdete ga v datoteki "
"<filename>COPYING</filename> v datoteki &kig; izvorno drevo ali povezavo do "
"licence v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>O &kig;</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1022
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to contribute ?"
msgstr "Kako prispevati?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1023
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any contributions are welcome. If you don't like the icons, or think that "
"the manual needs updating, or if you have this really cool macro that you "
"want to share with the world, do not hesitate to send it to me. Please note "
"that your contributions will be distributed under the terms of the &GNU; "
"<acronym>GPL</acronym>; you can find the terms of this license in the "
"<filename>COPYING</filename> file in the &kig; source tree, and in the <link "
"linkend=\"credits\">Credits and License</link> chapter in this manual."
msgstr ""
"Vsi prispevki so dobrodošli. Če vam ikone niso všeč ali menite, da je "
"priročnik treba posodobiti, ali če imate ta res kul makro, ki ga želite "
"deliti s svetom, mi ga ne oklevajte in mi ga pošljite. Upoštevajte, da bodo "
"vaši prispevki razdeljeni pod pogoji &GNU; <acronym>GPL</acronym>; pogoje te "
"licence najdete v datoteki <filename>COPYING</filename> v datoteki &kig; "
"izvornem drevesu in v poglavju <link linkend=\"credits\">Zasluge in licenca</"
"link> v tem priročniku."
